Lady Zhen

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Zhen Luo)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the wife of Cao Pi of Wei of the Three Kingdoms. For the empress, the wife of Cao Fang of Wei of the Three Kingdoms, see Empress Zhen (Cao Fang). For the noble consort of the Xianfeng Emperor, see Empress Dowager Ci'an.


Lady Zhen



A Qing dynasty illustration of Lady Zhen



